message: Why did the llama bring a ruler to bed? To measure how long he slept!
description: Full-time comedian and part-time llama enthusiast.

message: Why did the sausage go to school? To get smarter and become a witty Wiener!
description: Dedicated to spreading laughter, one sausage joke at a time.

message: Why did the fish tell jokes? Because it had a great sense of humor and wanted to make a splash!
description: Master of underwater stand-up comedy, making waves with hilarious punchlines.

message: What did one banana say to the other? 'You're a-peeling!'
description: Living life with a peel of laughter, bananas are my muse.

message: Why don't giraffes use social media? They prefer to stick their necks out in person!
description: Spreading laughter from the tallest heights, one long-necked joke at a time.

message: Why did the monkey like the banana? Because it found it a-peeling!
description: Bringing joy and mischief with every playful swing through the trees.

message: Why don't walruses ever play cards? They're always at the bottom of the deck!
description: Ocean's resident comedian, making marine life chuckle with his clever wordplay.
